body_html:
similar issue solved here by renaming

mv tensorflow-0.7.0-py2-none-linux_x86_64.whl tensorflow-0.7.0-cp27-none-linux_x86_64.whl or 
mv tensorflow-0.7.0-py2-none-linux_x86_64.whl tensorflow-0.7.0-py2-none-any.whl
sudo pip2 install --upgrade tensorflow-0.7.0-cp27-none-linux_x86_64.whl
and 
mv tensorflow-0.7.0-py3-none-linux_x86_64.whl tensorflow-0.7.0-cp35-none-linux_x86_64.whl
sudo pip3 install --upgrade tensorflow-0.7.0-cp35-none-linux_x86_64.whl
